<h3>7. Live Streaming (&ldquo;Momentum Live&rdquo;)</h3>
<p><strong>Backend: Complete. Frontend viewer: Built but not routed.</strong></p>

<h4>Admin (fully wired at /admin)</h4>
<ul>
<li>Create/edit/delete live sessions</li>
<li>Schedule clips with ordering and duration control</li>
<li>Feature clips during broadcast; manual clip advancement</li>
<li>Chat moderation (ban/delete messages)</li>
<li>Poll creation and management</li>
</ul>

<h4>Public Live API</h4>
<ul>
<li>Current session + viewer count; clip schedule</li>
<li>Live chat (post + read); viewer heartbeats</li>
<li>Polls (create, vote, results, end)</li>
</ul>

<h4>Scheduled Tasks (scheduled.ts)</h4>
<ul>
<li>Auto-advance live clips; trending score recalculation</li>
<li>Viewer cleanup, chat ban expiry, JamBase quota pruning</li>
</ul>

<p class="gap"><strong>Gap:</strong> LiveBroadcast.tsx (stream viewer + chat + polls) exists but is not mounted on any route. Live features are admin-accessible only today.</p>

