<hr>

<h2>Database Schema Summary</h2>
<p><strong>54 migrations</strong> &rarr; <strong>50+ tables</strong> on Cloudflare D1 (SQLite).</p>

<table>
<tr><th>Domain</th><th>Tables</th></tr>
<tr><td>Users</td><td>user_profiles, user_privacy_settings, user_bans, verification_requests, account_deletion_requests, profile_views, daily_active_users, user_device_tokens</td></tr>
<tr><td>Auth</td><td>email_accounts, email_sessions, email_password_resets, google_accounts, google_sessions, two_factor_auth, two_factor_verifications</td></tr>
<tr><td>Clips</td><td>clips, clip_likes, comments, saved_clips, clip_ratings, clip_shares, clip_flags, user_favorite_clips_by_artist</td></tr>
<tr><td>Social</td><td>follows, notifications</td></tr>
<tr><td>Artists/Venues</td><td>artists, venues, artist_tour_dates, user_favorite_artists, artist_pinned_clips, collaboration_requests</td></tr>
<tr><td>Live</td><td>live_sessions, live_session_clips, live_session_viewers, live_featured_clips, live_chat_messages, live_chat_bans, live_polls, live_poll_votes</td></tr>
<tr><td>Payments</td><td>subscriptions, transactions, payout_requests, affiliate_sales, affiliate_ticket_clicks</td></tr>
<tr><td>Gamification</td><td>user_points, point_transactions, badges, user_badges</td></tr>
<tr><td>Caching/Telemetry</td><td>jambase_api_usage, youtube_api_usage, youtube_response_cache, venue_logo_cache, clip_show_resolve_telemetry, api_performance_logs</td></tr>
</table>

<p><strong>Identity model:</strong> Most tables use mocha_user_id (TEXT). Auth tables use separate UUID primary keys. Only 3 enforced foreign keys (email/google session &rarr; account).</p>

<h3>Recent Migrations (45&ndash;54)</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>#</th><th>What it added</th></tr>
<tr><td>45</td><td>venues.jambase_id for stable JamBase venue lookups</td></tr>
<tr><td>46</td><td>clips.song_title, clips.song_slug for per-song hub pages</td></tr>
<tr><td>47</td><td>google_accounts and google_sessions for direct Google OAuth</td></tr>
<tr><td>48</td><td>email_accounts.google_sub for linking Google to email accounts</td></tr>
<tr><td>49</td><td>clips.genre_name, clips.genre_slug for genre hub pages</td></tr>
<tr><td>50</td><td>youtube_api_usage and youtube_response_cache</td></tr>
<tr><td>51</td><td>venue_logo_cache for permanent logo resolution</td></tr>
<tr><td>52</td><td>Data backfill: show_id from jambase_event_id</td></tr>
<tr><td>53</td><td>clips.event_title column + backfill</td></tr>
<tr><td>54</td><td>Index on clips.event_title for search/filtering</td></tr>
</table>

<hr>

<h2>API Surface</h2>
<p><strong>~170 HTTP routes</strong> in a single Hono app (src/worker/index.ts) plus WebSocket.</p>

<h3>Route Modules</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>Module</th><th>Domain</th></tr>
<tr><td>auth-endpoints.ts</td><td>Email auth</td></tr>
<tr><td>google-oauth.ts</td><td>Direct Google OAuth</td></tr>
<tr><td>clip-endpoints.ts</td><td>Clip CRUD</td></tr>
<tr><td>discovery-endpoints.ts</td><td>Discover feeds</td></tr>
<tr><td>artist-venue-pages.ts</td><td>Entity page payloads</td></tr>
<tr><td>song-page-endpoints.ts / genre-page-endpoints.ts</td><td>Song and genre hubs</td></tr>
<tr><td>jambase-endpoints.ts</td><td>JamBase proxy</td></tr>
<tr><td>youtube-endpoints.ts</td><td>YouTube proxy</td></tr>
<tr><td>stripe-endpoints.ts / stripe-webhooks.ts</td><td>Payments</td></tr>
<tr><td>ticketmaster-endpoints.ts</td><td>Events</td></tr>
<tr><td>google-maps-endpoints.ts</td><td>Geocoding</td></tr>
<tr><td>gamification-endpoints.ts</td><td>Points/badges</td></tr>
<tr><td>gdpr-endpoints.ts</td><td>Privacy compliance</td></tr>
<tr><td>moderation-endpoints.ts</td><td>Content moderation</td></tr>
<tr><td>analytics-endpoints.ts</td><td>Metrics</td></tr>
<tr><td>personalization-endpoints.ts</td><td>User prefs</td></tr>
<tr><td>live-polls-endpoints.ts</td><td>Live polls</td></tr>
<tr><td>collaboration-endpoints.ts</td><td>Artist collabs</td></tr>
<tr><td>follow-endpoints.ts / rating-endpoints.ts</td><td>Social graph, ratings</td></tr>
<tr><td>stream-endpoints.ts / resumable-upload-endpoints.ts</td><td>Video upload pipeline</td></tr>
<tr><td>music-recognition.ts</td><td>Song ID</td></tr>
<tr><td>scheduled.ts</td><td>Cron tasks</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Cross-cutting Concerns</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Rate limiting</strong> &mdash; per-IP/user buckets for auth, upload, search, JamBase, YouTube</li>
<li><strong>Performance headers</strong> &mdash; cache control via performance-utils.ts</li>
<li><strong>Validation</strong> &mdash; Zod schemas via @hono/zod-validator</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>Frontend Architecture</h2>

<h3>Active Routes (22)</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>Route</th><th>Page</th><th>Purpose</th></tr>
<tr><td>/</td><td>Home</td><td>Main feed (personalized when logged in)</td></tr>
<tr><td>/auth</td><td>Auth</td><td>Sign in/up (email + Google OAuth)</td></tr>
<tr><td>/auth/callback</td><td>AuthCallback</td><td>OAuth callback</td></tr>
<tr><td>/auth/reset-password</td><td>ResetPassword</td><td>Password reset</td></tr>
<tr><td>/onboarding</td><td>Onboarding</td><td>New-user setup</td></tr>
<tr><td>/upload</td><td>UploadClip</td><td>Full clip upload flow</td></tr>
<tr><td>/saved</td><td>SavedClips</td><td>Bookmarked clips</td></tr>
<tr><td>/liked</td><td>LikedClips</td><td>Liked clips feed</td></tr>
<tr><td>/discover</td><td>Discover</td><td>Search and browse</td></tr>
<tr><td>/users/:userId</td><td>UserProfile</td><td>Public/own profile</td></tr>
<tr><td>/artists/:artistName</td><td>ArtistPage</td><td>Artist hub</td></tr>
<tr><td>/venues/:venueName</td><td>VenuePage</td><td>Venue hub</td></tr>
<tr><td>/artists/.../songs/:songSlug</td><td>SongPage</td><td>Song clips under artist</td></tr>
<tr><td>/songs/:songSlug</td><td>GlobalSongPage</td><td>Cross-artist song clips</td></tr>
<tr><td>/genres/:genreSlug</td><td>GenrePage</td><td>Genre-filtered clips</td></tr>
<tr><td>/artists/.../shows/:showId/clips</td><td>ShowClips</td><td>Show-specific clips</td></tr>
<tr><td>/events/clips/:eventTitle</td><td>EventClips</td><td>Event-grouped clips</td></tr>
<tr><td>/admin</td><td>Admin</td><td>Admin dashboard</td></tr>
<tr><td>/analytics</td><td>Analytics</td><td>User analytics</td></tr>
<tr><td>/premium</td><td>&mdash;</td><td>Redirects to / (not launched)</td></tr>
<tr><td>*</td><td>NotFound</td><td>404 page</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>State Management</h3>
<p>No Redux, Zustand, or React Query. Three layers:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>AuthProvider</strong> (@getmocha/users-service) &mdash; session state</li>
<li><strong>React Context</strong> &mdash; MobileChromeContext, ClipUploadQueueContext, NotificationsContext</li>
<li><strong>36 custom hooks</strong> &mdash; domain data fetching with useState + fetch/apiFetch</li>
</ol>
<p>Cross-component sync via custom DOM events and localStorage caches.</p>

<h3>Key UI Patterns</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Mobile-first</strong> &mdash; bottom tab nav (Feed, Discover, Capture, Alerts, Profile)</li>
<li><strong>Dark concert aesthetic</strong> &mdash; momentum-ember, momentum-flare brand palette</li>
<li><strong>Immersive clip viewing</strong> &mdash; chrome hides during modal playback</li>
<li><strong>Background uploads</strong> &mdash; non-blocking share after capture</li>
</ul>

<hr>

